    "attributes": {
        "action": "Launch a campaign on HIV to tell the public that Undetectable = Untransmittable ",
        "additional_details": "The Government should create a national media campaign to quash over 30 years of stigma around HIV. The government spent \u00a35m in 1987 (the equivalent of \u00a313.2m in 2022) on the monolith advert. A new campaign from the Government does not need to cost the earth, if it uses those living with HIV to front the campaign.",
        "background": "After informing (scaring) the nation with its 1987 AIDS monolith TV advert, it is time for the Government to update the public on HIV and the advances in science with a campaign based around \"U=U\" (Undetectable = Untransmittable). ",
